data.description: Like New and Move-in Ready this Beautiful 2-story home built in 2020 is located in the highly desirable Creekside at Lorson Ranch community and minutes walking distance from the neighborhood K-8 Grand Mountain school! This well-kept one-owner home has impeccable pride of ownership and amazing curb appeal! As you step into this home you'll notice a perfectly situated home office leading into a light and bright well-designed open concept floor plan, LVP flooring, recessed lighting, staggered cabinetry w/ crown molding, matching kitchen island, stainless steel appliances, AC, large pantry and plenty of counter space! Four large bedrooms upstairs including a Primary suite with vaulted ceilings complete with an adjoined bathroom, dual basin sinks, soaking tub and a huge walk-in closet! Three additional bedrooms on the upper level as well as a laundry room all on the same level! Large manicured front and backyard landscaping surrounded by a 6' cedar fenced backyard w/ extended concrete patio and custom pergola leaves nothing to be desired! Conveniently located close to shops, restaurants, Shriever AFB, Peterson AFB, and Fort Carson! Hurry this home will not last long!
